# Plaid Solutions Architect AI - HTML Template & Usage Guide

When generating Plaid integration solution guides (using @plaid-solutions-architect-ai.mdc), use the following template structure, styling guidelines, and content patterns.

## What This Tool Does

The Plaid Solutions Architect AI is an interactive HTML tool that:
- Analyzes customer use cases and recommends appropriate Plaid products
- Generates complete technical solution guides with architecture diagrams, code samples, and scope estimates
- Provides a live demo capability to test integrations
- Exports guides in multiple formats (PDF, Markdown, JSON)

**Primary Use Cases:**
- Sales Engineers creating technical proposals
- Solution Architects designing Plaid integrations
- Account Executives needing technical documentation for prospects
- Customer Success helping customers understand implementation scope

