## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

**"Failed to fetch" error in Demo tab:**
- Backend not running or not deployed
- Check Backend URL in Advanced settings
- Verify CORS is enabled (already configured in demo-backend-server.js)

**Diagrams not rendering:**
- Mermaid.js failed to load
- Check browser console for errors
- Refresh page

**Code copy not working:**
- Browser clipboard permissions
- Try manual copy/paste
- Check browser console

**Products not detected correctly:**
- Use case description too vague
- Manually add/remove products using badges
- Guide will regenerate automatically

### Backend Deployment Issues

**Port binding error:**
- Backend uses `process.env.PORT || 3000`
- No changes needed for most platforms

**CORS errors:**
- CORS is enabled for all origins in backend
- Verify backend URL matches in HTML

**Dependencies not installing:**
- Check `package.json` is present
- Run `npm install` manually
- Verify Node.js version (14+)

